set_strict_shop

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_strict_shop -  This method sets the strictness of the shop, if the shop is strict it will not deal in items of other types at all.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_strict_shop(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the new strict value
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the strictness of the shop, if the shop is strict
it will not deal in items of other types at all.
.EP

